column2: SELECT m.objid, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1, m.apstar_id, m.apogee_id, a.apstar_id, params.*, paramerrs.*, elemsALL.* into mydb.apogeestar_photobj_aspcap from mydb.apogeestar_photobj AS m JOIN aspcapStar AS a ON m.apstar_id = a.apstar_id CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapParams (a.aspcap_id) params CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapParamErrs (a.aspcap_id) paramerrs CROSS APPLY dbo.fAspcapElemsAll (a.aspcap_id) elemsALL
